Package: meedyamanager
Version: 0.9.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgtk-4-1 (>= 4.12), libadwaita-1-0 (>= 1.4), libglib2.0-0 (>= 2.76)
Installed-Size: 12288
Maintainer: MWBM Partners Ltd <packaging@mwbm.co.uk>
Homepage: https://github.com/MWBMPartners/MeedyaManager
Description: Smart cross-platform media file manager and auto-organizer
 MeedyaManager monitors your media folders and automatically renames and
 organizes audio and video files according to user-defined rules — similar
 to MusicBee's auto-organize feature, but available on Windows, macOS,
 and Linux.
 .
 Features:
  - Real-time folder monitoring with file-lock awareness
  - 4-level media classification (group/format/class/quality)
  - Metadata lookup from 19 providers (MusicBrainz, Discogs, TMDB, etc.)
  - Cloud storage monitoring (OneDrive, Google Drive, Dropbox)
  - MusicBee-inspired rename template engine
  - Cover art display and tag editing
  - Dry-run preview before executing renames
